The scripts under install/ (terminal-tools, mise, github-cli, docker,
btop, fastfetch, lazygit, lazydocker, neovim, git-aliases, libraries) are
derived from Omakub's install/terminal scripts, adapted to run standalone
(no Omakub dependency) and to support Ubuntu 22.04 and 24.04.
